    • Method Detail

      • execute

        void execute(WorkerEnvironment workerEnv)
        This is the main point of entry for Twister2 jobs. Every job should implement this interface. When a job is submitted, a class implementing this interface gets instantiated and executed by Twister2. As the first thing in the execute method, users are expected to initialize the proper environment object: for batch jobs: BatchTSetEnvironment for streaming jobs: StreamingTSetEnvironment
